This map came about because I was bored by all the jailbreak maps which relied on wardens to be clever enough to come up with some way of making trivia interesting. I decided to make a map which had some games which were actually fun. I drew inspiration from mg_ski_mountain and built my map around the idea of having a ski resort for a prison. This map requires noblock to function properly. It was heavily tested on a 46 player server with a tickrate of 33 and an sv_airaccelerate of 300. It has more than 64 spawns. Games, areas and items include: *Ski *Surf *Race *Climb *Hot Potato *Four Chairs *Hockey *1v100 *Disco *Solitary *Armory *Defend the House Cabin *World's Smallest Box Cage *RC Helicopter *Some vents to armory *9 special items and weapons, including a musical grenade and an unlimited ammo deagle Credits Puck and hockey goals from ka_wn_icehockey Some custom textures made with bases from cgtextures.com, a sign from spencersnook.com Amazing trees, stumps and rocks from de_forest by the esteemed Robert Briscoe. Credit for the timers goes to Fibbs (original timer), vince (improved timer) and CartraxWolf (advanced timer). I modified it to count downwards and stop at 0 instead of counting up. I also created a miniature counter because the one provided did not shrink well. The hockey scoreboard and climb damage indicator are also heavily modified versions of the timer. Musical grenade by Adamfish, modified to toggle off and change songs when the holder jumps. Krassell's unlimited ammo prefab, heavily edited so it doesn't suck. Controllable helicopter by smurfi. Log cabin by Metz. Speakers by Di[M]aN Please feel free to send bugs, questions or suggestions This map was designed for the sG Jailbreak server - 174.36.231.16:27015 - joinsG.net Enjoy -thorgot

Fixed the doors that where too small and the spawns.

Holds 30 people, 10 on CT and 20 on T. 

There are 3 guns cells, 3 nade cells, one vent cell and several ways to rebel. Rebelling isn't too easy but not ridiculously hard either. A lot of the rebelling spots are somewhat hard to find and blend in well. 

The map is made to look like a hospital. The west (I think) wing upper floor is just for show and doesn't actually go anywhere, same with the bottom part a little further in. 

!lr room is in the basement and has Gun Toss and S4S and a good place for knife fighting and whatnot. Also contains a pool that doesn't actually do much but looks pretty. Doesn't have soccer because: 
* I've never seen a hospital with a soccer court.
* No one ever plays soccer in jail.

Really only contains the necessary stuff that is actually used frequently.

Here is my second Jailbreak map

Jail Up

Introduces New Types Of Cells

Cells: 12 cells that are lowered into the ground when the button is pressed the cells rise out of the ground.

VIP: TV w/ "moving picture", couch, plants, laser/fog switch

Pool: Very Deep Pool W/ Shower Room including steam

Last Request Room: Enough Room To Do Shot For Shot, Platform For Deagle Toss, enough room for race

Armory: Stocked Full Of fully armed weapons. Almost every weapon avalible is in armory

Infirmary: Just Walk In No Button To Press

Small Soccer Field: Behind Infirmary

Hidden Areas: There Are A Few Hidden Areas For The T's To Find

Cryptic Fortress
ba_jail_cryptic_fortress_v1

by: =(eGO)=™ Batterytime

Following are some features of the map:
-Armory: Contains many gun choices, including scouts, bullpups, aks, m4s, tmps, shotties, and autoshotties. There are three types of pistols, deagles, usps, and 5-7s.
-Cellblock and cells: cells are arranged in a 9x2 grid, 9 cells on each floor. Cells are large and very easy to hide in, but a cell lockdown (only for the cells) occurs at 6:00 after map start.
-ST Markers/Solitary: There are three c4/bombs in one of the solitary rooms. Ts can pick these up and they will be marked ST on top of their head for easy recognition of special treatment prisoners. Solitary cells doors are ct coded.
-Couch room: I don't really like to play the couch game, but it is there for nostalgic and decorative purposes. :P
-Park: playground and sandbox for hot lava, s4s glass arena, spray wall, and ct walkway.
-Hospital: window outwards to park, two story hospital
-Climb: Two climbs, dark and light climb, each has an ending spot that is visible from the ct walkway. Climb end teleports to couch room.
-Disco: Three songs to choose from, Over the Frail Dream, Exploration of Space, and Harder, Better, Faster Stronger Remix, from left to right in disco booth. Light options are off, laser/rave, and full light.
-Pool: Contains a pool/beach and a jacuzzi, as well as two showers
-Race/Maze: Forcefield across from disco teleports players to the maze, sorted by team so the ts go onto the race side and the cts go onto the ct "safe" side. CTs can see Ts while they are racing, but not the other way around. Once one player finishes race, the others have 15 seconds before getting killed.

Please leave any comments or suggestions. If you would like this map customized, please contact me at explosivecranberry@gmail.com.

~Batterytime
